title: Some of My Favorites from IUMA
description:
Some of My Favorites from IUMA, the Internet Underground Music Archive 
(now defunct, unfortunately).  Mostly gleaned from the New Age category 
at IUMA, but they are hard to pigeonhole so neatly.

All are at 128 kilobits per second except for Heaven\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\&#039;s Air 
at 160 kbps and Similar To Light at 192 kbps.
